746
00:29:31.030 --> 00:29:36.560
♪ ♪

747
00:29:42.130 --> 00:29:42.280
.

748
00:29:42.340 --> 00:29:43.440
- I was sleeping.

749
00:29:43.540 --> 00:29:45.900
Captain Braddock woke me up.

